this is 
    Open for extension and close for modification

    Open for extension- mekedi kiyanne aluthen class functions easily add karaganna puluwan wenna One 
    close for modification- class/module eka edit karanne naha bugs hoyagannakan

    meke saralawa kiyanne modification karanawanaw eka karanna puluwan wenna one but tina ewwa 
    edit karanna bari wenna one.eka thama meke principle eka.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DNT
    *enum 
        meka use karanne c# wala constant tiyaganna.

    *main with all eke tinne without using ocp meke wenne apita thawa invoice ekak add karanna one unama 
        invoice class eka edit karanna one ethakata ai e class eka debug karanna one.ocp kiyanne edit 
        karanne debug ekak awoth witharai eka hinda class eka edit karanna baha.

    *solution ekak widihata karanne aluthen ena functions new class ekaka dana eka ethakota e class eka 
        vitharai edit karanna one wenne.
    
    *meke virtual kiyala ganne override karanna puluwan wenne ethakota static ekedi meka use karanna baha.
        hugak welawata onema function ekak non-virtual ewa.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TIM
    *basic eka thamai Person class ekak hadala tinawa Employee class ekak hadala tinawa.Person kenek Employee
        kenek karanne account eke tina create function eken.
    
    *aluthen ekatuwena eka thamai eya manager , stuff da kiyana ewwa 

    *apita enum ekaka manager,stuff,executive eva liyala Employee eke isManager isStuff isExecutive liyala 
        eka false kiyala liyala tinawa. account eka hadana kota e Employee ge is eka true karanawanawa.
            mekata karanakota ocp vialate wenawa

    *mekedi karanne Person,account ekei interface hada ganna eka.ekata hetuwa thama dan manager account 
        ekak hadanna one kiyala kiyamu ekata karanna one manager kiyala class ekak hadaganna ita passe manager 
        account ekak hadaganna.   
    
    *mekedi karanna tinne aluthen add wena ewwa tinawane ewa nikan interface widihata ganna one.
        if else if kiyala ene ewa me principle eka use karala issella code ekata haniyak nowenna hadanna puluman